 * properties. The Stack component takes the same props as the {@link Frame} component
 * as well as a few additional interface defined below.
 *
 * @remarks
 * ```jsx
 * function MyComponent() {
 *   return (
 *     <Stack>
 *       <Frame />
 *       <Frame />
 *       <Frame />
 *     </Stack>
 *   )
 * }
 * ```
